
1.	Start the system when powered ON.
2.	Check time: Is it feeding time (08:00am or 06:00pm)?
  o	If no → wait and loop
  o	If yes → proceed.
3.	Check food availability.
  o	If Empty → send alert: Food is not available
  o	If Available → dispense food
4.	Wait 10 minutes after dispensing.
5.	Check weight:
  o	If weight decreased (pet ate) → success.
  o	If unchanged (pet did not eat) → send alert: Pet did not eat
6.	End process. 
